title: Stellar Escape v2.31
description:
With outstanding graphics and fantastic controls, prepare to embark on an awesome journey running for your life. Experience wicked combos that will keep your adrenaline pumping for sure!

You play the role of Elliot Black, a courier in the Beta sector. But after a quite irrational move, you are forced to flee for your safety. Travel through several different areas of the space station, until you finally reach your spaceship.

Features:

* Beautiful 3D graphics 
* OpenFeint leaderboard and achievements
* 15 challenging levels in 5 different environments
* Endless mode with two difficulties
* Intuitive and responsive controls

What's New:

- Share your score with friends on Facebook
